txt.en: Turned in a guild-pattern cutting board
The leader of the Woodworker's Guild has asked to create a cutting board for the Cook's Guild.
The crafting recipes you must create can be bartered for from the Improved Recipes vendor.\n\nMake a guild-pattern cutting board.
Turned in a guild-pattern cutting board

'[placeholder] I have a very important job for you! The Cook's guild is requesting cutting boards, and lots of them. This is an in-kind trade. Can you imagine the morsels they will send our way? Quickly! Go make cutting boards!'
